Palestinians say it is raining fire in Gaza, after Israel started [ground
operations](https://globalvoicesonline.org/2014/07/17/breaking-israel-begins-
ground-operations-in-gaza/) into the besieged enclave tonight.

Home to about 1.7 million Palestinians, Gaza is bordered by Israel on one side
and Egypt on another. Both borders are heavily controlled, leaving residents
with nowhere to run. Critics of Israel's occupation have described Gaza as an
open-air prison.

